19 Fraternity membership or upon the presentment of an application for
20 a Masonic Fraternity license plate authorized and approved by the
21 Grand Lodge of Oklahoma. The license plates shall be designed in
22 consultation with the Masonic Fraternities of Oklahoma and shall
23 contain the Masonic emblem;
