21 C. The fee for such plates shall be Fifteen Dollars ($15.00)
22 per year of renewal and shall be in addition to all other
23 registration fees provided by the Oklahoma Vehicle License and
24 Registration Act. Unless otherwise provided in this section, the
SENATE FLOOR VERSION - HB4266 SFLR Page 31
(Bold face denotes Committee Amendments)

1 fee shall be apportioned as follows: Eight Dollars ($8.00) per year
2 of renewal of the special license plate fee shall be deposited in
3 the Tax Commission Reimbursement Fund to be used for the
4 administration of the Oklahoma Vehicle License and Registration Act
5 and the remaining Seven Dollars ($7.00) per year of renewal of the
6 special license plate fee shall be apportioned as provided in
7 Section 1104 of this title. Beginning January 1, 2023, Eight
8 Dollars ($8.00) per year of renewal of the special license plate fee
9 shall be deposited in the Service Oklahoma Reimbursement Fund to be
10 used for the administration of the Oklahoma Vehicle License and
11 Registration Act and the remaining Seven Dollars ($7.00) per year of
12 renewal of the special license plate fee shall be apportioned as
13 provided in Section 1104 of this title.
14 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
